verse_part: for such and such a price
were constantly added to their number
they were cut to the quick
having received it in their turn
as he called on the Lord
they were coming out of them
when they had washed her body
and when I had fixed my gaze
You are out of your mind
when they had opened the door
that they be led away to execution
those who would lead him by the hand
when the meeting of the synagogue
when he had fixed his gaze
when they had brought them out
there used to spend their time
for me to put up with
image which fell down from heaven
and taken his leave of them
When he had gone back up
for a period of three years
and started on our way up
I was led by the hand
and proceeded to make his defense
you are out of your mind
and let ourselves be driven along
they began to jettison the cargo
When they had been brought safely through
